channel.title: Cryptchaosv1 [FIRST RELEASE]
channel.description:
THIS IS MY FIRST EVER SERVER AND RELEASED IT FOR A BASE FOR YOU GUYS :)
[b]I forgot to post it here its been on silab for a week or 2 so here it is! (Please no flame I know how some people on here can get -.-)[/b]
[b]OVER 300 DOWNLOADS![/b]
[size=5]FOR THE EXTREME NOOBS![/size] [code]When im compiling.. THe results are always: Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note:Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details.
Done![/code] [size=5]MEANS ITS WORKING PROPERLY![/size]
[b]Base Creator:[/b][i]Zykev2 -I USE ZYKEV2 ON [b]ALL[/b]FORUMS[/i]
[b]Server Name:[/b][i]Cryptchaos. Or C.C for short.[/i]
UPDATES LOG.
[i] - Made new home - Made new Smith - Added new NPC's to Home - Completed home - Completed Smith - Added new Starter. - Added new command ::mage - Fixed eating glitch - Added new Jad location - Added new thieving area - Added new Team pk - Completed Team pk - Added NPC's - Added Farcasting. - Switched Team pk to pk - Fixed xteletome and xteleto - Added WC - Fixed safezones (80%) - DBmini once you slay the last demon a darkbow appears in inv - 100% Safezones in Dbmini - 100% Safezones game wide - Added new colors to right click - Added NPC's to Level 1 and 5 of Dbmini (talking) - Fixed Dbmini Monsters health - Black demon (Level 5 of dbmini) is agressive -Added new shoping area's -Added Edgeville pking -Added new pk spot -Added ::runes (Basic element runes) -Added ::bruens (Ancient runes x1000) -Added new wood cutting place -Chopping tree's no longer gives money it gives correct logs -Added pretty good timers for WC -Added Firemaking (Burns all logs) -All portals work -Added farcasting with Bows! -Added drop party area -NPC's behind portals at home -Made Fires disappear and give ashes (Only visible to the person making fire going to make it disappear for everyone) -Added new interface! -Added Godsword stance -Illegal charecters (SYIpkpker, SYI, ~, ect) Are now blocked and will be banned!
PLEASE NOTE THIS IS A MUCH SMALLER LIST ALOT OF SMALLER UPDATES WERE MADE[/i]
Commands
[b]Owner commands (Co-owner)[/b] [i]::banuser ::ipban ::pickup ::kick ::pnpc ::xrichie ::xteleto ::xteletome ::xteleall ::notedbarrows ::players ::ground ::master ::pure ::empty ::sweet ::rich[/i]
[b]Administrator Commands[/b] [i]::banuser ::ipban ::kick ::pnpc ::xteleto ::xteletome ::notedbarrows ::brunes2 (10000 Barrage Runes) ::players ::ground ::empty ::sweet ::rich ::runes[/i]
[b]Moderator Commands[/b] [i]::banuser ::kick ::xteleto ::xteletome ::notedbarrows ::starter ::brunes (1000 Barrage runes) ::players ::ground ::empty ::rich ::runes [/i]
[b]Regular Commands[/b] [i]::starter ::players ::ground ::brunes (1000 barrage runes) ::empty ::runes[/i]
(Note: Only Owner/Co-owners are able to do ::master and ::pure)
if you cannot fill out a answer please put N/A [hr] [hr]
IN-GAME PICTURES

[b]Home Portals (Party peet leads to party room where you can have drop party's)[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/Portals-1.jpg[/img]

[b]1v1 PK[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/newpk-1.jpg[/img]
[b]GS mini (Money Maker)[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/gsmini1-1.jpg[/img]
[b]TEAM WEST BLOCK OFF[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/westblock-1.jpg[/img]
[b]Smith[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/smith-1-1.jpg[/img]
[b]Jad[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/jad-1-1.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/dark1-1.jpg[/img]
[b]Darkbow mini-game level 2[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/dark2-1.jpg[/img]
[b]Darkbow mini-game level 3[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/dark3-1.jpg[/img]
[b]Darkbow mini-game level 4[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/dark4-1.jpg[/img]
[b]Darkbow mini-game level 5 (Boss)[/b] [img]http://i284.photobucket.com/albums/ll37/zykev2/dark5-1.jpg[/img]
======================================
Notes: [i]This is my first ever release of a server and actually my first ever server. I will continue to make new versions and updated versions. The next verison is Cryptchaos v1.5 which will have much cleaner files as I have to admit they are not the most tidy because its my first server, more glitches fixed, different locations on some places ect. All server bases I use come with 'roflmao456 auto restarter' all ready configured for you to use just click it and set when you want your server to be restarted. Please read the 'README!' .txt file on the base after downloading Thanks and I hope you like it![/i]
[b]Cryptchaos v2 is already in the making and I'm going to release soon, it will have a lot more features WAY cleaner files I'm sorry there a bit big and a little messy but most will be better in v2. Hope you guys like it.[/b]
-------------------------------
